</P>
<P>
Employees 3,000 
</P>
<P>
Assets $132.3 million 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Common stock 1.95 million shares 
</P>
<P>
52-week high $40.25 
</P>
<P>
52-week low $20.625 
</P>
<P>
Monday close $25.25, down $6.625 
</P>
<P>
Source: Standard &amp; Poor's, Associated Press 
</P>
</TEXT>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
